Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:06.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:22.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:24.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:24.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you might have this bruise for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Kunisaki-kun, Kamio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:03.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem.
Comment: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:04.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: It's not a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It started when Kano was still a little girl.
Comment: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:22.98,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:23.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the first summer after our mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:24.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:25.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, balloons!
Comment: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:26.62,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,BALLOONS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, if I bought one, would I be able to fly in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:06.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If one balloon could lift a person, the stall would have flown away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:11.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then that means I can fly through the sky if I have lots of  balloons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:20.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, maybe then you could fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can only afford one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's one balloon, we'll just have to blow it up really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, it'll be able to lift much more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we won't be able to buy anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.06,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,BALLOONS\NTARGET
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:45.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Comment: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:48.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:53.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kano always wanted to fly through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because she believed that she could see her mother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told her that her mother was in the sky, watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Neither Father nor I could tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:15.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that her mother was no longer around anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:18.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:22.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what happened?
Comment: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:27.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:27.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's playing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We put the feather back and went home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't go to where Mommy is anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The following morning, Kano started acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She became afraid of bright lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:45.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and she started wandering around outside in a daze,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,mumbling nonsense to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One night, Kano was gone before I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I rushed to look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:02.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found her in the examination room, pressing a scalpel to her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught her in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:48.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized then; she wasn't Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like someone else was pretending to be Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a case of multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a magical bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep wearing it until you're an adult, you'll be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, no matter what happens, never take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the one who gave Kano the bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she ever tried to unconsciously cut her wrist again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd see the bandana and come to her senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano doesn't really remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There never was any such thing as magic.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: There was never such a thing as magic. Which phrases better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to follow in my father's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:51.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I became a doctor, I'd be able to cure Kano's illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that feather that Kano touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's been there at the shrine for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the shrine-keeper doesn't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's the curse of that feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a doctor, I can't accept that kind of explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's possible that the feather was a psychological trigger for her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Kano was suffering from a lot of stress after losing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably the root cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:23.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to Kirishima-san's place today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go visit Kano later too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad you made a new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:39.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I had another dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream of flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this dream, I was traveling further and further back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:54.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I was mourning in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:59.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were mourning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, my body was soaring through the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:06.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why I felt so sad surrounded by such beautiful, comforting breezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about you personally.
Comment: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward phrase above. (Original: It has nothing to do with you personally.)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not smiling, I also feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:18.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:25.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:43.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:52.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:53.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you picking up stuff like that to collect garbage or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:56.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:57.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Collecting interesting things from places like this is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most pathetic hobby ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:01.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:06.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to play day in and day out. You're in a very enviable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty much like that too, aren't you, Yukito Kunisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:20.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'm on my way to my job right now to work hard.
Comment: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some sound I can't hear. Ony? or Oy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:36.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that, by any chance, Tohno's mom?
Comment: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some sound I can't hear. Ony? or Oy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:47.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:54.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, call Minagi over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's lonely all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:01.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:03.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:13.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:21.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a walk with Michiru.
Comment: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.45,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma Cycling Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:38.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you with Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:43.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Michiru say anything about the person who was with me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:46.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:00.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I once helped her with a big cart of groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:03.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the two of you are rather similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:04.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a fragment of that person's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:05.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.67,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko pikopiko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:16.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll scrub you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:17.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko... Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing well.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Better phrase than 'high spirits'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yukito-kun. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It seems that I caused you troubled yesterday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:25.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came, Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of work for you to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kano-san taking a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:52.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to rest because of what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:57.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:59.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yukito-kun, I am writing this to you because I think you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally decided to go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that it will make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that I will meet the girl you are looking for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know how long it will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I will definitely bring her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd be grateful if you could help Onee-chan until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know she is under a lot of stress.
Comment: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: She's actually really pushing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}P.S. I'm really sorry about the bruise on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.24,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Pikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:35.56,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopikopikopiko pikopikopikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.69,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko. Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko Piko Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:05.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no superficial wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be life-threatening,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:22.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but what on Earth happened?
Comment: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: 'on earth' -> 'exactly'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she tried to go up to the sky from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:27.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, my emotions are acting up,
Comment: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,better word for acting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:41.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like I'm nostalgic... or sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:44.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay Kano down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Shiraho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please listen to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember - it was a beautiful autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:53.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My husband and I had our first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She had a birthmark on her right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:58.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The villagers said it was ominous, but we never paid them any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Yakumo cried, I sang him a lullaby that I had learned from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:10.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yakumo would always stop crying, but that day, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that the feather was a charm sent by God for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:13.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A war started, and my husband, like many others, never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:19.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone in this village pick up a shining feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is cursed! Anyone who has touched it should step forward and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That night, I fled from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:47.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I arrived at this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The chief priest of the shrine was very kind to us outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that Yakumo and I would be able to start a new life in this peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, that summer, an epidemic spread through the village, killing many.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Priest, how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:10.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:16.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His fever will come down in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:22.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the villagers believe the two of you brought the epidemic to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:38.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to invite the two of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:59.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We worship a divine idol here.
Comment: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Here we worship the miko-gami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:15.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The idol gives a sign to those who bring bad fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:19.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the villagers discover her birthmark, they will demand her to be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to sacrifice him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:46.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this land, we have always averted disasters by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:55.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:16:03.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only treasure my husband left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you will be killed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:17.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:24.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What mother would kill her own child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:27.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it might destroy the world, what mother could bear to kill her own child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:31.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:36.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, somehow, save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:53.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:01.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:03.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:29.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Potato too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And a new friend I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of wish that I were that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things are too hard for you, you can come with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember much about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I might have cut your life short,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:18.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving birth to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:24.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:33.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so live happily down there.
Comment: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono ko no kawaisa kagirinaya\NThere is no end to the ways this child is so dear
Comment: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten ni tatoeba hoshi no kazu\NLike the number of stars in the heavens
Comment: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:45.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yama dewa ki no kazu, kaya no kazu\NThe number of trees in the mountains
Comment: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yama dewa ki no kazu, kaya no kazu\NThe number of grasses in the field
Comment: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:52.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obana karukaya, hagi, kikyou\NFlowering broomsedge, bush clover, bellflowers
Comment: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana kusa, chigusa no kazu yorimo\NMore than the flowers of autumn
Comment: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:03.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana kusa, chigusa no kazu yorimo\NMore than the number of all the flowering plants
Comment: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:04.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijina kono ko ga nenne suru\NMy precious child is sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san, you saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:30.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:39.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:45.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:49.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:59.16,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:04.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was that feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:08.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Comment: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:17.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:22.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I met Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:25.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go to where she was,
Comment: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:26.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I couldn't go with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:35.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was able to thank her, just like Yukito-kun told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:54.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it soar into the sky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:59.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.61,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:13.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just get in the way, so I'm always playing by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:23.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't accept reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she chose to live in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:27.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Comment: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.58,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5
